game.name: Courier Havoc
game.description: In this really fun game you have to work as a courier driver and deliver all the packages to the right customers. Pick them up in your van from the courier headquarters and follow the arrow to find the right parking spot. Then enjoy an exciting mini-game in which you have to make sure all your customers are satisfied. During each level you have to pay attention to your life bar and your timer. Complete all eight incredible levels that you have available. Have a great time!
